column5: Normally CE07SHSM PCO2A is on DCL11 but is installed on DCL12 for this deployment
Normally CE07SHSM NUTNR is on DCL12 but is installed on DCL11 for this deployment
Normally CE07SHSM NUTNR is on DCL27 but is installed on DCL26 for this deployment
Normally CE07SHSM SPKIR is on DCL27 but is installed on DCL26 for this deployment
For this deployment all VEL3D are internally logging with no connection to the DCL. Thus, no VEL3D data until recovery.
The data for the DOSTA is available in */dcl37/ctdbp2.  Uses record stream ctdbp_cdef_dcl_ce_dosta.
